name: ragebait
description: The project is a memecoin on Solana, launched via pump.fun, which has been CTO'd later after the launch. The CTO has been ongoing for 3 months now. The token is about the commonly used term/trend "ragebaiting" which has gone popular in 2025. "ragebaiting" is kind of like "trolling" for Gen Z. It is a memecoin with a community who post memes about ragebaiting etc. The long term plan is to grow the community more and get more content/funny memes made with real artists to promote the token.
